        <title>[教程向]基于Termux在安卓手机上安装Kali</title>
        <link>https://www.retr0.qzz.io/p/%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B%E5%90%91%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8Etermux%E5%9C%A8%E5%AE%89%E5%8D%93%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85kali/</link>
